The bug can be seen on level 29 if you stand on the left set of blocks that has a single gold in it. The enemies will get stuck on the second ladder which has a pole on the right side.The Apple II, Atari 8-bit, Commodore 64, and naturally the VIC-20 versions of the game have this bug since they were all made by Broderbund. But interestingly so does the Hudson Soft NES port. The later Macintosh version, which is otherwise a direct port of the Apple II code, fixed it. The IBM-PC version didn't have this bug because it was rewritten with the memory layout
